title: Lidar maker Luminar declares bankruptcy; Quantum Computing to buy subsidiary
description:
Lidar maker Luminar has filed for Chapter 11 and plans to sell off its assets after Volvo terminated a key contract.

The post Lidar maker Luminar declares bankruptcy; Quantum Computing to buy subsidiary appeared first on The Robot Report.
